'''Dambas'''
[[File:Campfire_scar_08319.JPG|thumb|Dambasku waa hadhaaga [[dab]]ka.]]

'''Dambas''' ([[ingiriis]]: Ash) waa budo cad, khafiif ah oo ka soo hadhay [[dab]] [[wakhti]] shidnaa. 
Dambasku waa hadhaaga ugu dambeeya wax kasta oo la gubo. 

Dambasku wuxuu ka kooban yahay kimikooyin badan. Dambaska [[dhuxul|duxusha]] waxay ka samaysan tahay [[Isku dhis]]yada [[Kaalshiyaam|kaalshiyaam-kaarboonayt]] iyo [[Kaalshiyaam|kaalshiyaam-ogsaydh]]. 

Waxaa jira noocyo badan oo kala duwan oo ''dambas'' ah taas oo ku xidhan shayga [[dab|la gubey]]. 
Tusaale ahaan, [[sigaar|dambaska sigaarka]], [[dhuxul|dambaska dhuxusha]] iwm. 

Guud ahaan, dambaska [[dhuxul|dhuxusha]] [[dhir]]ta waxaa loo isticmaalaa in [[caro|carada]] [[beer]]aha lagu daadiyo si loogu nafaqeeyo. 

Wadanka [[Soomaaliya]] dhexdiisa, dambaska waxaa lagu dhex daraa [[buuri]]ga [[af]]ka la gashado si dhadhanka u bedelo. 

